  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe created this policy to outline a few guidelines for all employees who work remotely and handle company equipment. You may work remotely on a permanent or temporary basis depending on your personal circumstances and business needs. Please be mindful that not all positions are appropriate or feasible for remote work. If you work remotely, you must make sure that your work areas are safe and meet safety standards.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003EIf you\u2019re a remote employee, we\u2019ll provide you with equipment that\u2019s essential to your job duties, such as a laptop and monitor.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
